info.description:
PyBuilder is a python program which makes compiling exe's simpler.
The program has a nice GUI interface and uses py2exe to build the exe's.

*NOTE* PyBuilder requires Python and Py2exe
info.name: PyBuilder-for-Py2exe
info.platform:
Windows/windows like. Wrote in Python but uses windows commands, and only builds
exe's for windows or windows like systems.
info.summary: A tool to asist in compiling python scripts with py2exe
